## ğŸ”§ Configuration

### Environment Variables (.env)
```env
NODE_ENV=development
PORT=5000
ADMIN_EMAIL=admin@dhronepredicts.com
ADMIN_PASSWORD=dhrone123
REACT_APP_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api
```

### Production Deployment

1. **Render.com**: Connect your repository and set environment variables
2. **Vercel**: Deploy frontend separately, backend on Render/Heroku
3. **Netlify**: Deploy frontend, use serverless functions for API

## ğŸ“± Integration with Main Website

Your main website can fetch prediction data directly from the JSON files:

```javascript
// Example fetch for Free Tips
fetch('https://your-domain.com/data/freeTips.json')
  .then(response => response.json())
  .then(data => {
    // Display predictions on your website
    console.log(data);
  });
```

